Author: TinyLoaf
Text: I’m so proud of you! 30 days is incredible.   Sorry to hear you’re going through some rough shit, but it’s admirable that you didn’t turn to binging your emotions. Good luck! Keep going :)

Author: Anaanonymous
Text: Well congratulations on 30 days purge free!  As for the other stuff, we can only control how we react. I hope things fall into place for you
